      "desc": "Eighty feet of plywood and mahogany powered by three Packard engines. She's fast, fragile, and carries enough torpedoes to sink a cruiser \u2014 if she can get close enough without being blown apart. PT boats fought at night, at speed, in waters too shallow for destroyers.",
