      "desc": "Fifty thousand tons of Krupp steel, eight fifteen-inch guns, and the most feared warship in the Atlantic. She was designed to break the Royal Navy's blockade and terrorise the convoy routes. She managed one sortie. It took the entire Home Fleet to stop her.",
